So they are in the scene, but the `excalidrawRef.current.getFiles()` call just returns an empty object so the list of files doesn't get persisted to local storage.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/47948499/159602584-3c8baae1-7c03-4f11-9b4c-2fcdf3e83dc2.png)


Any ideas? Thanks!

